      "created_at": "2018-11-26T00:07:40.331Z",
      "cooked": "<p>lufta per naften dhe ujin, distopi e paraqitur te mad max fury road<br>\n</p><div class=\"lazyYT\" data-youtube-id=\"hEJnMQG9ev8\" data-youtube-title=\"Mad Max: Fury Road - Official Main Trailer [HD]\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"270\" data-parameters=\"feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque\"></div>",
