      "created_at": "2018-11-27T06:05:58.234Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Liria ne imagjinaten e perlindjes kaure eshte nje femer e bukur .kur Te kem nge do te bej studim me themeli mbi natyren diskriminuese te bartesve te supozuar te idealeve me larta te njerezise ndaj shemtaraqeve te cilet perbejne 99.9% te banoreve te globit <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/blush.png?v=9\" title=\":blush:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":blush:\"><br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/d/d052b4ae90a2c2eae51870d0bd8a7be3b56d1d6c.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/d052b4ae90a2c2eae51870d0bd8a7be3b56d1d6c\" title=\"D9122032-29D6-4B6B-B831-43DBDAE62935.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d052b4ae90a2c2eae51870d0bd8a7be3b56d1d6c_2_800x641.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"800\" height=\"641\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d052b4ae90a2c2eae51870d0bd8a7be3b56d1d6c_2_800x641.jpeg, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d052b4ae90a2c2eae51870d0bd8a7be3b56d1d6c_2_1200x961.jpeg 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d052b4ae90a2c2eae51870d0bd8a7be3b56d1d6c_2_1600x1282.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d052b4ae90a2c2eae51870d0bd8a7be3b56d1d6c_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">D9122032-29D6-4B6B-B831-43DBDAE62935.jpeg</span><span class=\"informations\">2972×2385 2.37 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
