      "created_at": "2018-11-27T08:17:43.581Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Nje tjeter rast i ralle qe tregon visionin e Shen Benardit, te cilit, nderkohe qe po luste Madonna del Latte, ajo i sprucoi qumeshtin nga gjiri i saj drejt e ne goje:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/d/da9fcbb59a65d84652772952d8ff78566ef82e2e.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/da9fcbb59a65d84652772952d8ff78566ef82e2e\" title=\"f.366Cano%20Alonso%202.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/d/da9fcbb59a65d84652772952d8ff78566ef82e2e.jpeg\" width=\"543\" height=\"800\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/da9fcbb59a65d84652772952d8ff78566ef82e2e_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">f.366Cano%20Alonso%202.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">550×809 78.1 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
