      "cooked": "<p>si gjithnje <strong><em>Eros e Thanatos</em></strong>, nuk ke nga e lu ngambrapen.</p>\n<p>Qe ku e keni edhe skulpturen me titulli Nënë Rusi me cica dhe  shpate ne dore, me dimensione te njejta sa Statuja e Lirise amerkane:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0e7a95601b0e7c214f7651510b22739808f08da3.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/0e7a95601b0e7c214f7651510b22739808f08da3\" title=\"la_statua_della_madre_russia_sulla_collina_mamaev_a_volgograd.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0e7a95601b0e7c214f7651510b22739808f08da3.jpeg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0e7a95601b0e7c214f7651510b22739808f08da3_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">la_statua_della_madre_russia_sulla_collina_mamaev_a_volgograd.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1000×667 118 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
